name: Lia
description:
Lia is my niece, daughter of a very close brother.


It was very thrilling to see this new life coming to earth, turning my brother into a father.


This music is about that.


Davi Fonseca - Composition, arrangement and piano.
Alexandre Silva - Clarinet
Natália Mitre - Vibraphone
Camila Rocha - Acustic Bass
Yuri Vellasco - Drums
Alexandre Andrés - C flute
